・Mathクラス

・ルート
puts Math.sqrt(36)
= 6

・log
puts Math.log(1)
= 0

・計算上の小数点以下
puts 10 / 7
= 1
puts 10 / 7.0
=1.4285714285714286

[xx.0]を付けると、小数点部分も計算する。

・入力機能(改行)
puts "Enter Your Name: "
name = gets
puts ("Hello " + name + ", you are cool!")
=
Enter Your Name:
keita
Hello keita
, you are cool!      改行される・・・

・入力機能(改行しないver)
puts "Enter Your Name: "
name = gets.chomp()
puts ("Hello " + name + ", you are cool!")
=
Enter Your Name:
keita
Hello keita, you are cool!

・数値入力
puts "Enter a number: "
num1 = gets.chomp()
puts "Enter another number"
num2 = gets.chomp()
puts (num1 + num2)
=
Enter a number:
12
Enter another number
34
1234  文字扱い

・数値入力　　.to_i = 整数(小数点切り捨て)　.to_f = 少数含む
puts "Enter a number: "
num1 = gets.chomp()
puts "Enter another number"
num2 = gets.chomp()
puts (num1.to_i + num2.to_i)
=
Enter a number:
12
Enter another number
34
46

・入力と出力
puts "Enter a color: "
color = gets.chomp()
puts "Enter a plural noun: "
plural_noun = gets.chomp()
puts "Enter a celebrity: "
celebrity = gets.chomp()

puts ("Rose are "+ color)
puts (plural_noun + " are blue")
puts ("I love " + celebrity)
=
Enter a color:
Blue
Enter a plural noun:
apple
Enter a celebrity:
Emma Watson
Rose are Blue
apple are blue
I love Emma Watson

・配列
