puts friends
=
Kevin
Karen
Oscar
puts friends[0]
puts friends[-2]
=
Kevin
Karen
puts friends[0, 2] 　0以上2未満
Kevin
Karen

・配列の上書き
friends[0] = "Dwight"
puts friends[0]
=
Dwight

・配列の初期化
friends = Array.new
puts friends[0]
=
   (空っぽ)

・配列と空っぽ空間
friends[0] = "Michael"
friends[5] = "Holly"
puts friends
=
Michael




Holly

・配列のカウント
friends = Array["Kevin", "Karen", "Oscar"]
puts friends.length()
=
3

・真偽チェック
puts friends.include? "Karen"
=
true

・配列の逆転
puts friends.reverse()
=
Oscar
Karen
Kevin

・配列　アルファベット順
friends = Array["Kevin", "Oscar", "Andy", "Karen"]
puts friends.sort()
=
Andy
Karen
Kevin
Oscar

・ハッシュ
states = {
  "Pennsylvania" => "PA",
  "New York" => "NY",
  "Oregon" => "OR"
}
puts states
= {"Pennsylvania"=>"PA", "New York"=>"NY", "Oregon"=>"OR"}
puts states["New York"]
= NY

states = {
  :Pennsylvania => "PA",
  "New York" => "NY",
  "Oregon" => "OR"
}
puts states[:Pennsylvania]
= PA

states = {
  1 => "PA",
  "New York" => "NY",
  "Oregon" => "OR"
}

puts states[1]
= PA

・メソッド(関数)
def sayhi()
  puts "Hello user"
end

sayhi
= Hello user

・関数と変数
def sayhi(name, age)
  puts ("Hello " + name + ", you are " + age.to_s)
end

sayhi("Mike", 73)
= Hello Mike, you are 73

・変数の初期設定
def sayhi(name="no name", age=-1)
  puts ("Hello " + name + ", you are " + age.to_s)
end

sayhi("Mike", 73)
sayhi()
=
Hello Mike, you are 73
Hello no name, you are -1

・リターン文
def cube(num)
  num * num * num
end
puts cube(3)
= 27

・優先度
ef cube(num)
  num * num * num
  5
end
puts cube(3)
= 5　　　27は消えてしまう・・・

・return(関数の終わり)
def cube(num)
  return num * num * num,
  puts "hello"
end
puts cube(3)
= 27　　　　　helloは表示されない


・if文
ismale = false

if ismale
  puts "You are male"
else
  puts "You are not male"
end
= You are not male


ismale = true
istall = false

if ismale and istall
  puts "You are a tall male"
elsif ismale and !istall
  puts "You are short male"
elsif !ismale and istall
  puts "You are not male but tall"
else
  puts "You are not male and not tall"
end
= You are short male


・if文(比較演算子)
def max(num1, num2, num3)
  if num1 >= num2 and num1 >= num3
    return num1
  elsif num2 >= num1 and num2 >= num3
    return num2
  else
    return num3
  end
 end
puts max(10,12,5)
= 12

